// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1553 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: abaf618a-7351-5968-be98-07c154a41d9a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
